patch=1,EE,201E2A2C,extended,00000000

[Super Insanely Fast Firing Rate]
author=BigBossman
description=This affects all weapons. Your standard machine gun can go through its rounds in a matter of seconds. This also works on any weapon you can pick up such as the shotgun, rocket launcher, & plasma gun. The amazing this is how much faster your ammo will run out while using this code.
patch=1,EE,106883D2,extended,00000001

[Super Insanely Fast Speed]
author=BigBossman
description=Makes it EXTREMELY hard to control your character because he moves so fast. In fact, it appears as if on some stages, you might even be able to walk through certain walls. At certain points, you might also take damage depending on how fast you're moving & how fast you fall or move into something.
patch=1,EE,106883C2,extended,00000001

[Win Most Deathmatches]
author=BigBossman
description=Mostly works for campaign mode. Even if another player gets the required number of frags, you'll be declared the winner even though your opponent(s) did.
patch=1,EE,10688348,extended,00000000

